      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch nodohs Isra-\nelu Jerobeama Grzhku deht/ kas\ngrehkojes/ un Israëlu darrijs\ngrehkoht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad zehlehs Jerobeama\nSeewa/ un nogahje/ un nahze\nuhß Tirzu. Kad nu winna us ta\nNamma Sleekſni nahze/ tad\nnomirre tas Puifsis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee aprakke winnu/ un\nwiſs Israëls schehlojahs pahr to/\npehz ta KUNGA Wahrdn/ ko\nwiꞥſch bij runnajs zaue fatwu\nKalpu to Praweetu Akiju.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un kas wehl no Jerobea-\nma Leetahm atteek/ ka tas kar-\nrojs/ un ka tas waldijs/ redſi/\ntas irr rakſtihts eekſch to Israëta\nKehniau Laiku-Grahmatas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas Laiks/ kamehr\nJerobeams Kehniaſch bijis/ irr\ndiwidesmits un diwi Gaddi/ un\ntas aismitge ar faweem Teh-\nweem/ un winna Dehts Nadabs\ntappe par Kehniau winna Weetâ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Rekabeams Salania-\nna Dehts waldija eekſch Juudas.\nTscheirdefinits un weenu Gad-\ndu bija Rekabeams wezz/ kad tas\npar Kehniau tappe/ un waldija\nfeptispadeſinits Gaddus Jeru-\nsalemes Bilsſahtâ/ ko tas KUNGS\nbij iſwehlejs/ fawn Wahrdn tur\nlikt/ no wiſſahn Israëka Ziltim.\nUn winna Mahtes Wahrdn bija\nNaëma/ weena Ammoniterene.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Juha darrija/ kas\ntain KUNGAM ne patikke/ un\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tee usdarrija few ar-\nridsan Augſtunus/ un uszeltas\nBildes/ un kuplus Meschus/ ue-\nikkatru augstu Pakalnu/ un ap-\npalsch wiſſeem fatteem Rohkeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ir Mauzineeki bija ta-\nSemme/ un darrija pehz wiſ-\nfahm Negantibahm to Pagamu/\nko tas KUNGS Israëta Behr-\nnu Preekschâ bij tsdsinnis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un peektâ Gaddâ ta Keh-\nnira Rekabeama/ zehlehs Sisaks\ntas Egiptes Kehniaſch us aug-\ntchu prett Jerusalemi/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un nehme ta KUNGA\nNamma Mantas/ un ta Keh-\nnira Namma Mantas nobst/\nwiſsch nehme wiſſu nobſt/ ir-\nwiſsch nehme wiſſas preekschtur-\nramas Bruunas no Selta/ ko\nSalaimans bij lizzis darriht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tas Kehniaſch Rekabe-\nans darrija winnu Weetâ\npreekschturramas Bruunas na\nWarra/ un dewe tahs to Pils-\nKatta- Wihro Wirfneeku Roh-\nkâ/ kas ta Kehniau Namma Dur-\nwis apfargaja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kad nu tas Kehniaſch ue-\nta KUNGA Nammu gabje/\ntad nehfe tee Pils-Katta-Wihro\ntahs/ un pehz nehfe tee tahs atka-\nto Pils-Katta-Wihru Raimbari-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kas nu wehl atteek no\nRekabeama Leetahm/ un wiſſ/\nko wiſſch irr darrijs/ redſi/ tas\n"
    }
  ],
